OL,3,CBoy, 17, charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed outside mosque
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy has been charged
OL,7,Fwith murder after a teenager was
OL,8,Fstabbed outside a mosque in Smethwick.
OL,10,FZeshan Afzal, 18, was found with
OL,11,Fserious stab wounds outside Jamia
OL,12,FMasjid mosque on Oldbury Road shortly
OL,13,Fbefore 9pm on 20 February. He died
OL,14,Fshortly afterwards.
OL,16,FThe 17-year-old, who can't be named
OL,17,Fbecause of his age, was due to appear
OL,18,Fat Wolverhampton Magistrates Court
OL,19,Fthis morning for a first hearing.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
