OL,3,CBoy, 17, charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed outside mosque
OL,6,FTwo other men, aged 19 and 22, were
OL,7,Ftaken to hospital following the
OL,8,Fincident with injuries not thought to
OL,9,Fbe life threatening.
OL,11,FPolice said they are not treating the
OL,12,Fincident as religiously or racially
OL,13,Faggravated.
OL,15,FA GoFundMe site has been set up to
OL,16,Fsupport Zeshan's family.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
