OL,3,CBoy, 17, charged with murder after
OL,4,Cteenager stabbed outside mosque
OL,6,FA statement on the page read: "This
OL,7,FRamadan, a month of mercy,
OL,8,Fforgiveness, and immense reward, we
OL,9,Fwere tested in the most heartbreaking
OL,10,Fway.
OL,12,F"Our beloved brother was tragically
OL,13,Ftaken from us during this sacred month
OL,14,F` a time when the gates of Jannah are
OL,15,Fopen and deeds are multiplied.
OL,17,F"He was a son, a brother, a friend,
OL,18,Fand a light in our lives.J"His
OL,19,Fkindness, generosity, and laughter
OL,20,Ftouched everyone who knew him."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
